about.summary: Common object storage frontend that supports dictionary-style access, object serialization and compression, and multiple storage and caching backends.

name: shove
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "shove" %}
{% set version = "0.6.6" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/f5/c6/75b6d46b76b43626d7da946331827a7ccb38f2b4683808c74f3eff2519a5/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.bz2
  sha256: f1c643b5c68f45ad3a3fb6f39aa7f1a9221d0c387a135df06123990f83a734ec

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - stuf >=0.9.14

test:
  imports:
    - shove

about:
  home: https://bitbucket.org/lcrees/shove/
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Common object storage frontend that supports dictionary-style access, object serialization and compression, and multiple storage and caching backends.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - npavlovikj
